   emission and Kalbach systematic angular distr.                 1634 1451
   (code PCROSS by R.Capote et al)                                1634 1451
 - Hybrid Monte Carlo preequilibrium model(M.Blann)               1634 1451
   (code DDHMS by M.Chadwick, mod. by B.V.Carlson)                1634 1451
