 - Built-in input parameter files, such as masses,                1634 1451
   level density, discrete levels, fission barriers               1634 1451
   and gamma strength functions based on the RIPL                 1634 1451
   library [RIPL]                                                 1634 1451
 - Automatic retrieval of experimental data from the              1634 1451
   EXFOR library                                                  1634 1451
 - ENDF-6 formatting (code EMPEND by A.Trkov)                     1634 1451
   coupled to graphical presentation capabilities                 1634 1451
   (code ZVView by V. Zerkin) through the chain of                1634 1451
   PrePro codes by D. Cullen                                      1634 1451
 - ENDF checking codes (CHECKR, FIZCON, PSYCHE)                   1634 1451
 - Highly automated fitting of optical model                      1634 1451
   parameters (by B.V. Carlson)                                   1634 1451
 - KALMAN code for fitting experimental data and                  1634 1451
